column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_r, p.dered_g, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote,          zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon,          zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger            FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN zoo2MainSpecz AS zms ON p.objid = zms.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=# and zms.nvote >= # and zms.p_cw > # and zms.t0#_bar_a0#_bar_flag = #
